arm is hurt and you
have a sprained ankle.

39
00:03:23,359 --> 00:03:24,960
I already bandaged you up.

40
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:28,320
Later, drink some tonic and
get some sunlight to recover.

41
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:31,639
It's already late now.
Have a rest.

42
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,279
Don't listen to him.

43
